(firstQuint)A Study of 1592U89 and Ethanol When Given Together to HIV-Infected Patients.

 Patients are randomized to one of the following three regimens: Regimen 1: 1592U89 alone.

 Regimen 2: pure grain alcohol diluted in orange juice.

 Regimen 3: 1592U89 plus pure grain alcohol diluted in orange juice.

 Treatment is administered weekly for 3 weeks.

